data.description: Investor alert! Rent, renovate or house hack. Move in ready 3 bed / 1.75 bath main home 1,500 sqft + 1 bed/ 1 bath ADU apartment 220 sqft + 1200 sqft of unfinished basement! On 6,356 sqft corner lot zoned NR3.  Earn $3,250/mo for the house & $1,295/mo for the apartment for a total proforma annual income of $54,540. NOI approximately $45,200 for a solid 5.2% CAP with opportunity to increase income via finishing the basement, an addition or build a DADU. Or – make this home shine for a handsome ROI.  All in an unbeatable N Seattle location minutes to I-5, North Seattle College, Northgate, light rail station, Carkeek Park, shopping & dining. You'll want to make this opportunity yours! Buyer to verify all information, zoning & sqft.
